name: Uint8Array.BYTES_PER_ELEMENT
description: Returns a number value of the element size. 1 in the case of Uint8Array.

name: Uint8Array.prototype.BYTES_PER_ELEMENT
description: Returns a number value of the element size. 1 in the case of a Uint8Array.

name: Uint8Array.prototype.constructor
description: The constructor function that created the instance object. For Uint8Array instances, the initial value is the Uint8Array constructor.
